Field Label:
REDCap sub-project
e.g., Data Model, Code List

JSON version for this sub-project
A counter for how many times the sub-project JSON file has been updated and regenerated. Indicates the 4th version of the Data Model, or the 2nd version of the Code List.

JSON File of the Data Model
A machine-readable summary of either the data model or the code lists project in JavaScript Object Notation (JSON) format. These JSON files can be used as input for scripts and external software. They also serve to archive prior states of the data model.
